    84	- **Extension systems.** Four parallel subsystems: pi-coding-agent extensions; GSD ecosystem extensions; workflow plugins; skills. Skills is *one of four*, not the primary surface. Source: SYNTHESIS.md F2 + slice-4 audit §2 CG-1 + (vi) addendum.
