   134	
   135	**Two-step conditional.** Step-1 cross-vendor codex GPT-5.5 high baseline pass under minimal lens-spec; Step-2 same-vendor adversarial-auditor-xhigh stress + differential analysis fires *only if* Step-1 returns Class C candidates. Pre-commit to floor + escalate on evidence (mirrors B2 selective-audit discipline at DECISION-SPACE.md §1.12).
