    12	# gsd-2 Uplift Initiative — Staging Artifact
    13	
    14	This document stages the gsd-2 uplift initiative forward. It is not the scoping document — scoping happens through first-wave exploration + second-wave design work. This document records the goal as articulated, the open framing questions, the inputs available, and the first-wave plan.
    15	
